Package com.example.scanpal

Class Attendee

java.lang.Object
com.example.scanpal.Attendee
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Attendee extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an attendee of an event. This class encapsulates the data related to a user's participation in an event, including their RSVP status and whether they have checked in. Instances of this class are used to manage and track event attendees' interactions.
